    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisites: </em>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-feats.zcLRLULjWtEGvaUb]{Crossbow Expert}</p><p>Your time with hand crossbows has increased your skill with the weapon. You have mastered the ability to use two crossbows at once giving you the following abilities:</p><ul><li>Ability to craft and use the hand crossbow add-on, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-items.BNDXS5iOfkcBKS9E]{Automatic Reloader of Hand Crossbows (A.R.C.H.)}</li><li>Able to draw and stow two hand crossbows at the same time.</li><li>When using the Crossbow Expert feat to make an attack as a bonus action, the bonus action instead allows 2 attacks. Second bonus action attack must be made from the off-hand crossbow.</li></ul>",
